◆ AgentKey() [5/5]

template<typename KeyType >
IonicSecurity::SDK::AgentKey::AgentKey ( KeyType *  pKey)
inlineprotected

Initializes the underlying unmanaged object.

Parameters
[in]pKeyUnmanaged ISAgentKey object.

IMPORTANT: The AgentKey object takes ownership of the provided key pointer passed into this constructor. Also, keep in the mind that the key pointer may be pointing to a sub-class of ISAgentKey. To help simplify the process of marshalling the various key types, the ToUnmanaged and FromUnmanaged functions are templated on the concrete key type.
